metadata.name: The Unbeatable
metadata.description:
Peach × Bourke’s Parrot


She knows there is no Tohgenkyo,like a paradise or Shangri-La in the world, but she struggles to find her own personal Tohgenkyo.


She is flexible with a smile, yet she never forgets to have hidden passionate feelings inside.


No matter what anyone may not understand, no matter what anyone may say, if you act with your core, you will always be invincible under the sun.


Always cherish your thoughts and feelings.


The language of peach  is The Unbeatable and  unequaled qualities.
